2. PROPRIETARY RIGHTS

   The Software contains the following proprietary innovations:

   a) 4-Gate Financial News Classification System (البوابات الأربع)
      — Automated classification of financial news into tradeable (Path A),
        macro (Path B), and scarce-info (Path C) categories based on
        tradability potential and actionable value.

   b) Unified Single-Call AI Processor (المعالج الموحد)
      — A method for processing financial news from a source language to a
        target publication language using a single AI API call to produce
        translation, classification, and financial analysis simultaneously.

   c) 6-Slide Automated Infographic Generation System (نظام الإنفوغرافيك الستي)
      — Automated transformation of financial news/reports into interactive
        6-slide visual infographics with Hero, Story, Data, Scenarios,
        Assets, and Recommendations slides, including ECharts visualizations.

   d) Arabic Financial Translation Post-Processor (معالج الترجمة العربية)
      — 70+ rule-based correction system for AI-generated Arabic financial
        translations, including company name transliteration, financial
        terminology correction, and anti-fabrication validation.

   e) Multi-Provider AI Cascade System (نظام مزودي الذكاء الاصطناعي المتسلسل)
      — 11-provider AI cascade with per-provider circuit breakers, automatic
        failover, degraded mode operation, and provider health monitoring.

   f) Pipeline Resilience Architecture (هندسة مرونة الأنابيب)
      — 10-layer resilience system including watchdog timers, smart reset,
        external cron-based recovery, health guardian, and degraded mode.

   The above innovations are protected under applicable intellectual property
   laws, including but not limited to copyright, trade secret, and patent law.
   Pending patent applications may exist for one or more of these innovations.

